  "title": "Super Hold Water-base Liquid Adhesive",
  "body_html": "<p><meta charset=\"utf-8\"><span data-mce-fragment=\"1\">Water-based liquid adhesive aimed at attaching hair prostheses or other hair systems, such as wigs and hair extensions, to the scalp. The result is matte, which gives a more natural finish, leaving the hair root loose and dull while providing an extra strong hold.</span></p>\n<p>\u00a0</p>\n<h5 class=\"et_pb_toggle_title\">Advantages</h5>\n<div class=\"et_pb_toggle_content clearfix\">\n<p><img height=\"3\" width=\"44\" alt=\"\" src=\"https://luxhair.es/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/line_luxhair_2.png\" class=\"wp-image-145 alignnone size-full\"></p>\n<ul>\n<li>Matte and no-shine finish.</li>\n<li>Loos Hair root.</li>\n<li>Extra resistance to water, perspiration, and high temperatures.</li>\n<li>Long-lasting hold: Approximately 6 days with touch-up.</li>\n<li>The perfect solution for intensive physical activities.</li>\n<li>Specific formulation for hair systems such as hairpieces, wigs, and extensions.</li>\n</ul>\n<p>\u00a0<br></p>\n<h5 class=\"et_pb_toggle_title\">Format</h5>\n<div class=\"et_pb_toggle_content clearfix\">\n<p><img class=\"wp-image-145 alignnone size-full\" src=\"https://luxhair.es/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/line_luxhair_2.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"44\" height=\"3\"></p>\n<p>Quantity: 38 ml.</p>\n<p>\u00a0<br></p>\n<h5 class=\"et_pb_toggle_title\">Recommendations for use</h5>\n<div class=\"et_pb_toggle_content clearfix\">\n<p><img class=\"wp-image-145 alignnone size-full\" src=\"https://luxhair.es/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/line_luxhair_2.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"44\" height=\"3\"></p>\n<ul>\n<li>Apply to the scalp and not to the hair system.</li>\n<li>Apply to the outer edge of the desired area to be bonded.\u00a0Then spread the product evenly, applying the right amount to create a thin layer.</li>\n<li>Applying at least 2 or 3 layers is highly recommended, allowing the glue to dry 2-3 minutes between each coat application.</li>\n<li>Allow the glue to dry for a few minutes before attaching your capillary system.</li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<ul></ul>",
